data.description: Location, Location! Single family home Across from Cedarcrest golf course in Marysville, nestled into a quiet culdesac, Terrific concrete walkway leads you to a covered entry front door. Vaulted ceilings with decorative ledges lends height to the space. Bright and sunny glass doors off of the kitchen to the roomy level yard. Gas forced air heat, hot water tank. Ceiling fans and appliances stay. Loan on the house is an FHA assumable loan at 2.8%, you will get a huge discount at this rate.
